data.description: Circle marks the spot deep in the heart of AH, walking distance to Paloma Blanca, Bird bakery and Cambridge. This beautiful contemporary Townhome boasts of a very low maintenance, lock and leave type home. As you enter through the private gated courtyard and the 8ft entry door you are met with beautiful hardwood floors soaring 20 ft ceiling, light filled living area. moving into the generous dinning area with bar. Kitchen boast quartz countertops 36" SS gas range, new dishwasher, new disposer, wall of custom cabinetry with pullout drawers. Recessed lighting throughout, making your way upstairs you enter the spacious master suite with coffee bar area and private balcony the beautiful marble bath features a spa shower and personal area. 2nd bedroom has built in shelving and murphy bed. Other features include hidden safe room, pully system storage and tons of shelving in garage New metal roof New windows, Solar panels (owned)
